Message_HelpRequest (&502)
#Parent MSG_
+ 20	Mouse x
+ 24	Mouse y
+ 28	Button state
+ 32	Window handle, or -1 if no window
+ 36	Icon handle, or -1 if no icon
 
The !Help application sends out this message.

If you want to give some simple help on the given window/icon, then reply with a <HelpReply=>Msg_503> message.
#Line
See <PRM 3, page 244=>PRM-3:244>.
